\b JET_InsertName&Date.jsx\par
\b0 A Javascript for Adobe Illustrator by James E. Talmage\par
\par
Purpose:\par
This script adds the active document's file name and the current timestamp (date & time) at the text cursor position within a textframe object. \par
\par
To Use:\par
With an Illustrator document open, use the Text Tool to create a textframe object. This can be a textframe of any kind (PointType, AreaType, PathType).\par
The text editing cursor (the blinking text "I-beam") must be active in the textframe.\par
Run the script.\par
The script inserts the document's name and the current date into the textframe.\par
